milestones.description: Hansie Cronje has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (50) in an innings in ODIs for SA, going past Andrew Hudson's 46
This is the highest match aggregate (474) involving teams Australia & South Africa in ODIs
Adrian Kuiper has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for SA, going past Hansie Cronje's 3
